{"tid":739381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【倫敦金騙案】商罪科拉2金融公司高層 其一運作如常","createTime":"2018-07-12T05:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T06:01:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca04c199f7bdc40b0b6f83e02177f93b6b354028","tid":739381,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180712/large/1531372072_cd22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180712%2Flarge%2F1531372072_cd22.jpg&h=a79f1d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n針對以美人計或美男計手法行騙的倫敦金騙案，警方商業罪案調查科人員，連同多個部門，昨日展開代號「斷風」（SPLITFLASH）行動，搗破一個懷疑「倫敦金」騙案集團，警方帶同爆破工具，先後搜查北角電氣道183號「灝天金融集團」以及灣仔告士打道151號「天裕控股集團」的辦公室，撿走大批文件及現金等證物，行動中共拘捕17男9女，年齡介乎18至53歲，涉嫌串謀詐騙。( <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2uca6E6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uca6E6&d=HtNzjlSW6o2zHjPDy%2Fl7aP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=854d5f32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2uca6E6</a> )<br />\n<br />\n今日《蘋果》到灣仔的「天裕控股集團」辦公室，欲了解事件，甫出電梯發現佔全層的辦公室，雖然「燈光火著」，卻「人去留空」，並無職員上班。而位於北角的「灝天金融集團」，《蘋果》未能直接抵達其13樓的辦公室，只能到其14樓的另一個寫字樓，14樓有職員如常上班，對於公司有人涉及詐騙事件，職員表示不會評論，著《蘋果》向13樓的職員查詢。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，警方昨日的行動，拘捕多名涉案人士和兩間公司的高層，據悉當中包括一名53歲姓楊的灝天金融高層。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180712/58432362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F58432362&d=HtNzjlSW6o2zHjPDy%2Fl7aP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=45baa783\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F58432362&h=b1bf271c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180712/58432362</a>"},{"pid":"ee6acd21f60b13de8fbd37f223bc4e0f1d2e6f7f","tid":739381,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"幾時到張家輝賣廣告嗰間？"},{"pid":"c50fe03a1d985260377dad019ba1d8f59977d8fe","tid":739381,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 倫敦金可恥<br />\n但d比人呃既咁撚蠢, 警方幫佢起返d錢又點, 佢轉個頭咪又係第個呃左<br />\n幾撚蠢先會信呢d野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cadf867d8bf027f236ff8ed607037e1113fa6e3","tid":739381,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:19:14.000Z","msg":"唔係有600幾個全職架咩，去哂邊"},{"pid":"0e355ef8452c4b0a9098af19b3f418d7910ec99a","tid":739381,"uid":86337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"ken lau 比人拉左未"},{"pid":"e10f4fd4d3e8c40f3320e1e2dafb532cd64bbf80","tid":739381,"uid":161021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"人地生果都開晒名<br />\n屌你老母方向名都唔開<br />\n真1係落廣告大晒<br />\n咪撚做新聞喇"},{"pid":"78246139aef8d9c85450589b46acded3611add77","tid":739381,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e10f4fd4d3e8c40f3320e1e2dafb532cd64bbf80","tid":739381,"uid":161021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:00:09.000Z","msg":"人地生果都開晒名<br />\n屌你老母方向名都唔開<br />\n真1係落廣告大晒<br />\n咪撚做新聞喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:01:26.000Z","msg":"罷睇毒果！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}